{
  "stem": "21354.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And our cases were dispatched to be collected in the port of Antwerp, Holland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there they remained.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Antwerp in Holland.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything was dispatched for emigration to America.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had obtained our tickets.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had our affidavits.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were just waiting for our number.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were in numbers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Americans would accept so many per year, and we were waiting for our number to come up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "War started before our number came up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our cases had been sent in advance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything was in Antwerp port-- in a free port-- ready to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I say ready to go, don't imagine that we had 50 large cases.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had perhaps three or four cases.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A sewing machine, little bit of furniture, clothing, and whatever my father needed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody wanted us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We tried everywhere.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They tried Cuba, they tried China, they tried everywhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jews were then anxious to leave, to leave the best-- wherever they could.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody wanted us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One did hear rumors and the minute you-- you-- you had some information, you went to the consulate.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People often sat outside the consulate all night waiting for the consulate to open to find information, to find somewhere to go.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It became-- became rather distant, not in a-- an enemy-- not a-- not a-- not a hostile feeling towards us, but we had very little contact with the German community?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To give you an example, on the same landing where we lived, the family opposite us, he was a great stamp collector, and so was I.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Great stamp collector.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had about 200 stamps, but he had 10,000.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I spent many a day and evening with him, he explaining his stamp collection and I learned a great lot.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After '33 or '34, this contact stopped.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
